.SH NAME
.PP
hsh - Simple shell emulator
.PP
.SH SYNOPSIS
#include "shell.h"

hsh [options] [command | file]

.SH OPTIONS
.PP
Most shell commands works on this shell

.SH EXIT
.PP
Entring exit will quit the shell and it also takes a status option

